{"title":"场院的歌","authors":["木青"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":12,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"场院的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高高的谷垛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"围成金城一座，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是我们的场院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里面充满快乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不信，你听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有许多动听的歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圆圆的脱谷场上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石滚辘辘地碾过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像一张大唱片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从早到晚广播！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里有："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逗人乐的小曲儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脆亮的吆喝；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里有："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子的大笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们的嬉乐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可顶招人听的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是扬场时的金豆落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真像一股股甘泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流过心窝！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的场院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"确实有无限的快乐！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}